  ('dietitian-moex-01308', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '周先生，40歲，身高170公分，體重89公斤，健檢時初次發現空腹血糖180mg/dL；平日早餐多 不吃，午餐不定時，晚餐則多為應酬，喜喝含糖飲料。下列「營養診斷」的敘述，何者不符合「PES」 的邏輯與定義？', '["P：血糖值異常；E：外食頻率高；S：空腹血糖180mg/dL", "P：肥胖；E：BMI>30；S：喜歡喝含糖飲料", "P：醣類攝取不一致；E：營養相關知識不足；S：三餐規律性差", "P：營養相關知識不足；E：新診斷為糖尿病；S：不了解所喝飲料的含糖量，以及未能定時定 量進食"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "397cf22c480a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "18a33b1169b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01309', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-110-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關甜味劑的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["糖醇（sugaralcohols）的glycemicindex大於白米飯", "阿斯巴甜（Aspartame）屬於無熱量的甜味劑", "等量果糖的甜度大於蔗糖", "1克糖醇（sugaralcohols）可提供4大卡的熱量"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "397cf22c480a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "18a33b1169b6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
